title: Wall Street Breakfast July 21: Microsoft Cuts Job Listings; Google Pausing Hiring
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Microsoft reportedly cuts job listings in Azure, security. Google pausing hiring for two weeks - report.  Biden unveils plans to expand offshore wind; no climate emergency declaration. Tesla aims for record production in back half of the year. Catch today’s WSB article here.
